{"tid":2360442,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"海外港人創立嘅政治刊物《自由港》","createTime":"2021-01-09T18:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T18:13:55.000Z","uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bcde2d2955b583ac1024c24c780b958d4f7b434e","tid":2360442,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T18:13:55.000Z","msg":"《自由港 Harbour of Freedom》是一本由一群海外港人創立的政治刊物。主要刊登各方面不同的論述及評論，以及不同海外抗爭者的專訪。<br />\n<br />\n雖然身處海外，但我們希望能略盡棉力，建立一個能夠暢所欲言，能夠自由講的避風塘。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HarbourofFreedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHarbourofFreedom&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=d42df645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HarbourofFreedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>入面嘅文章幾高質，見大家提起未有得睇嘅如水，就推介下呢個tg都睇到嘅免費刊物<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}